text: Welcome to the study! The goal for each of the 4 discussions is for you to attempt to reach a consensus on the given topic. Each discussion will be in a new channel and there will be an "I agree!” message like the one above that will be ‘pinned’, meaning it can be found quickly under the “Details” and “Pinned Items” section, right of screen. On Mobile devices this is found by tapping the drop down bar with the channel name. When you believe the topic of discussion has reached a satisfactory conclusion and you agree with it, please give this “I agree!” message a ‘thumbs up’. If at any point you are not satisfied with the discussion, please remove the “thumbs up”. If you have any difficulty with anything, you can message me privately at any time via the “Direct messages” section, left of screen.
